question: Give me all dissertations and thesis proposals supervised by Dr. Jane Smith.
sql_query1:
SELECT Students.FullName
FROM Students
WHERE (Students.Academic_Writing = "Dissertation" OR Students.Academic_Writing = "Thesis Proposal") AND Students.Academic_Supervisor = "Dr. Jane Smith"
sql_query2:
SELECT Students.FullName
FROM Students
WHERE Students.Academic_Writing = "Dissertation" OR Students.Academic_Writing = "Thesis Proposal" AND Students.Academic_Supervisor = "Dr. Jane Smith"
interpretation1: Show all the dissertations supervised by Dr. Jane Smith, also show the thesis proposals she has supervised.
interpretation2: List all the dissertations, also show the thesis proposals supervised by Dr. Jane Smith.
